{
  "texts": [
    "In this regard, it could be beneficial to include LLMs that have been specifically adapted or \"fine-tuned\" to accommodate certain fields of study or areas of interest.",
    "In this work, we introduced a platform named LEAP that utilizes LLMs, currently models offered by OpenAI, to provide research-based feedback know to support students in various aspects of SRL, including cognition, metacognition, and motivation.",
    "This platform simplifies the interaction between teachers and LLMs, enabling them to easily create tasks that should stimulate SRL in students via fine prompting.",
    "Another use is the creation of various task and feedback types to research methods of providing formative feedback to verify their effectiveness for SLR.",
    "We hold the conviction that the integration of LLMs into education is a promising avenue with the potential to revolutionize teaching and learning practices."
  ]
}